replies.reviewContent: Dear Faryal, we are so sorry to hear that your experience with our product was less than satisfactory and we highly regret the inconvenience caused. It was an uncommon instance and we'll do better in the future. We've also contacted you in this regard through call and we would like to inform you again that your refund has been issued to you in your daraz wallet. You are requested to give us a chance to win your heart again.
